    public abstract class ActorPrivateMessageEventBase<A extends Actor>
extends ActorMessageEventBase<A>
implements PrivateEvent
    Abstract base class for events involving an Actor and have a message and are private messages. Use the helper events if you want to listen to events involving either.
    See Also:
    ActorEvent, MessageEvent, PrivateEvent
